---
import Container from '../ui/Container.astro';
import Section from '../ui/Section.astro';
---

<Section id="process" background="dark">
  <Container>
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="text-sm sm:text-base font-mono text-cyan-400 tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">
        Cómo Trabajamos
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-300 mb-6">
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 via-cyan-300 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Nuestro Proceso
        </span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="relative">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div class="relative mb-6 group">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-cyan-500/70">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">01</span>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute top-1/2 -right-8 w-8 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/50 to-transparent hidden lg:block"></div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-300 mb-3">
              Levantamiento de Requerimientos
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Análisis detallado de sistemas actuales y definición precisa de las necesidades del cliente.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div class="relative mb-6 group">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-purple-500/70">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">02</span>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute top-1/2 -right-8 w-8 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500/50 to-transparent hidden lg:block"></div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-300 mb-3">
              Prototipo
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Diseño basado en información recopilada, creando modelos interactivos para validación.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div class="relative mb-6 group">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-cyan-500/70">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">03</span>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute top-1/2 -right-8 w-8 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/50 to-transparent hidden lg:block"></div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-300 mb-3">
              Desarrollo
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Implementación de la solución con las mejores prácticas y tecnologías del mercado.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div class="relative mb-6 group">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-purple-500/70">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">04</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-300 mb-3">
              Evaluación
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Pruebas exhaustivas, validación de resultados y entrega final con documentación completa.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
        Nuestras soluciones de software son adaptables a diversos sectores, optimizando procesos e impulsando la transformación digital en industrias textil, industrial, comercial y de servicios.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Section>
